Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个旋律…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.63,0:00:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是尾形游纪的女儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.57,0:00:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个天才尾形的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说这次是她的初次演出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.44,0:01:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像舞台的换场一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.69,0:01:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2025年 被称为GGP的反抗组织一夜间统领了世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.01,0:01:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级大国和反抗组织
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.10,0:01:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仇视心与巨大的战力差距
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.27,0:01:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GPP凭藉着新战力的投入颠覆了战局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得了历史性的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.21,0:01:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 这些英雄们的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未能被世人所见证
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是埋没在了“历史性胜利”这一词汇中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就从前台褪去了踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.06,0:01:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之后对新世界秩序的构想降临了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥漫着敌意的武装力量 报复的连锁反应
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及它的扩大…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到希望 灰色的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,革命 新的秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就算是那个已经在变化着的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也无缘触及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.61,0:02:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我依着母亲的叮嘱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舞台上将上天赋予我的生命拚命的跳着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这光 这感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在这个舞台上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才感受到自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帷幕在不觉中落下了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:57.70,LOGO1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}极影&蔷薇园
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:57.70,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}极影&蔷薇园
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:59.87,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Squeez'n step on it hard
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:59.87,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}跨上机车 马力全开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:03.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try to feet my heart beat
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:03.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}试着去感受心的律动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:06.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,High,as high as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:06.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}飞跃吧！尽你所能！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:10.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All your blood will turn to fountain water
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:10.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}血液沸腾有如泉涌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:13.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by plot in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:13.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大千世界，我们的周遭布满陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:17.44,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash away the stain of blood with tears
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:17.44,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}用泪水洗去血染的污点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:20.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot look,or they will spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:20.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}让双眼避开所有的蛊惑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:24.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wind of fuego will lead us through
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:24.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"烈焰"之风会引领我们向前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:41.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:41.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真实 我与它们融与一体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:45.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found guide-in line in the raging world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:45.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在波涛汹涌的世界里找寻指引
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:49.26,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:49.26,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}举目看 天湛蓝 纵然世界狂乱不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:50.52,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ride on Back
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:50.52,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仍有背骑的身影穿梭其间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:53.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we need is your sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:53.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我们需要的是你们的共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:56.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We make the history of our own
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:56.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一同去创造属于我们的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:04:59.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:04:59.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真实 我与它们融与一体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:07.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
